{"content": "I need to multiply 251 \u00d7 228 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 251\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 162 + 45 + 1 = 208\u2081\u2080\n- 228\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 162 + 18 + 8 = 188\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 208 \u00d7 188 = 39,104\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 39104 \u00f7 9 = 4345 r 1\n- 4345 \u00f7 9 = 483 r 0\n- 483 \u00f7 9 = 53 r 6\n- 53 \u00f7 9 = 5 r 8\n- 5 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 5\n\nReading from bottom to top: **58601\u2089**\n\n58601", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 323}